c: 11
v: 109
t: "Nabiyow ama koros taqbudeh tanim deedal kinniimit maagaywaagitin, usun numtinwwellittek sa yaqbudeenim malon keenik duma ken abbobti aqbaduk sugte numtinwwellitteh innah tanim akke waytek, diggah nanu digaalák ken kah xagnisneh nan ken maglab dudda luk keenih aceenno keenik daggoysime kalah"